-------------+----------------------------------------------------------------
      smkban |  -.0775583    .008952    -8.66   0.000    -.0951061   -.0600106
       _cons |   .2895951   .0072619    39.88   0.000     .2753604    .3038298
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

